lines: 1. Wuonwa, gonywa gi gweth mari,Pong` chunywa gi mor gi kuwe;Miwa duto herruok mari,kethowa bende iwe.Miwa geno, miwa geno,Ka wawuotho e pinyni.
2. Wachiwo pak gi mor bende,Kuom weche mioronwa;Ka wamako chikni chutho,Wanabed e herani.Konywa timo, konywa timo,gi kinda nyaka ibi.
3. Ka wawuotho e piny kae,Ber wati ni In kende;konywa ka walu e yori,Kik wajogi, kik wawe.Bedi kodwa, bedi kodwa,Ka wawuok, bende kwake.
